'''托尼·巴罗'''（{{lang-en|'''Tony Barrow'''}}，1936年出生于英格兰[[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]]）是一位英国新闻发言人，在1962年到1968年期间为[[披头士乐队|披头士乐队]]工作<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.beatlelinks.net/forums/archive/index.php/t-7859.html|title= Tony Barrow on Beatles Audition Tape|accessdate= 2008-01-18|archive-date= 2019-09-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190901222156/http://www.beatlelinks.net/forums/archive/index.php/t-7859.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。他创造出了“{{lang|en|The Fab Four}}”这一短语，在早期的一份新闻稿中首次使用<ref>{{cite book |last=Barrow |first=Tony |title=John, Paul, George, Ringo & me: the real Beatles story |publisher=[[Da_Capo_Press|Da Capo Press]] |year=2006 |page=35 |isbn=978-1-56025-882-7 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=BNnzcGw8JQsC&lpg=PA258&dq=%22fab%20four%22%20nickname%20beatles&pg=PA35#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=July 19, 2011 |archive-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630102037/http://books.google.com/books?id=BNnzcGw8JQsC&lpg=PA258&dq=%22fab%20four%22%20nickname%20beatles&pg=PA35#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

